\c 15
\s Umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* ulethwa eJerusalema
\p
\v 1 Wasezenzela izindlu emzini kaDavida, walungisela umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu indawo, wawumisela ithente\x + 16.1. 2 Lan. 1.4.\x*.
\v 2 Ngalesosikhathi uDavida wathi: Kakho ongathwala umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu ngaphandle kwamaLevi, ngoba yiwo iN\nd kosi\nd* eyawakhethela ukuthwala umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu, lokuyikhonza kuze kube nininini\x + 15.15,26. Nani 4.2,15. 7.9. Dute. 10.8. 31.9.\x*.
\v 3 UDavida wasebuthanisa uIsrayeli wonke eJerusalema\x + 13.5. 1 Kho. 8.1.\x* ukuze benyuse umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* endaweni yawo ayeyilungisele wona\x + 15.1,12. 2 Sam. 6.17.\x*.
\v 4 UDavida wasebuthanisa amadodana kaAroni lamaLevi.
\v 5 Kumadodana kaKohathi\x + 6.1. 23.6. 6.16. Eks. 6.16. Nani 26.57.\x*, uUriyeli induna, labafowabo, ikhulu lamatshumi amabili.
\v 6 Kumadodana kaMerari, uAsaya induna, labafowabo, amakhulu amabili lamatshumi amabili\x + 6.1. 23.6. 6.16. Eks. 6.16. Nani 26.57.\x*.
\v 7 Kumadodana kaGerishoni, uJoweli induna, labafowabo, ikhulu lamatshumi amathathu\x + 6.1. 23.6. 6.16. Eks. 6.16. Nani 26.57.\x*.
\v 8 Kumadodana kaElizafani, uShemaya induna, labafowabo, amakhulu amabili\x + Nani 3.30. 2 Lan. 29.13. Eks. 6.22. Levi 10.4.\x*.
\v 9 Kumadodana kaHebroni\x + 6.18. Eks. 6.18.\x*, uEliyeli induna, labafowabo, amatshumi ayisificaminwembili.
\v 10 Kumadodana kaUziyeli, uAminadaba induna, labafowabo, ikhulu letshumi lambili\x + 6.18. Eks. 6.18.\x*.
\v 11 UDavida wasebiza oZadoki\x + 6.8. 16.39.\x* loAbhiyatha abapristi\x + 1 Sam. 22.20. 1 Kho. 2.26.\x*, lamaLevi, oUriyeli, uAsaya, loJoweli, uShemaya, loEliyeli, loAminadaba\x + 15.5-10.\x*.
\v 12 Wasesithi kubo: Lizinhloko zaboyise bamaLevi; zingcweliseni lina labafowenu ukuze lenyuse umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + 2 Lan. 35.6.\x* \add endaweni\add* engiyilungisele wona\x + 15.1,12. 2 Sam. 6.17.\x*.
\v 13 Ngoba lina lalingekho kuqala\x + 13.7. 2 Sam. 6.3.\x*, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu yafohlela kithi, ngoba singayidinganga ngokwesimiso\x + 13.11. 2 Sam. 6.8.\x*.
\v 14 Ngakho abapristi lamaLevi bazingcwelisa ukwenyusa umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli.
\v 15 Abantwana bamaLevi basebethwala umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu, njengokulaya kukaMozisi ngokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\x + 15.2. Eks. 25.14.\x*\nd*, emahlombe abo ngemijabo phezu kwabo\x + Nani 4.10,12. 13.23.\x*.
\v 16 UDavida wasesithi ezinduneni zamaLevi zimise abafowabo, abahlabeleli, lezinto zokuhlabelela\x + 15.19-21,28. 13.8. 16.5,42. 25.1,6. 2 Lan. 5.12. 9.11. 20.28. 29.25. Ezra 3.10.\x* lezigubhu zezintambo\x + 15.19-21,28. 13.8. 16.5,42. 25.1,6. 2 Lan. 5.12. 9.11. 20.28. 29.25. Ezra 3.10.\x* lamachacho lezinsimbi ezincencethayo, bazizwakalise, ngokuphakamisa ilizwi ngentokozo\x + 15.19-21,28. 13.8. 16.5,42. 25.1,6. 2 Lan. 5.12. 9.11. 20.28. 29.25. Ezra 3.10.\x*.
\v 17 AmaLevi asemisa uHemani indodana kaJoweli\x + 6.33.\x*, lakubafowabo uAsafi indodana kaBerekiya, lemadodaneni kaMerari abafowabo\x + 6.39.\x* uEthani indodana kaKushaya\x + 6.44.\x*.
\v 18 Njalo kanye labo abafowabo besigaba sesibili: OZekhariya, uBeni, loJahaziyeli, loShemiramothi, loJehiyeli, loUni, uEliyabi, loBhenaya\x + 15.21.\x*, loMahaseya, loMathithiya, loElifelehu, loMikineya, loObedi-Edoma, loJeyiyeli, abalindi bamasango.
\v 19 Abahlabeleli oHemani, uAsafi, loEthani bazizwakalisa-ke ngensimbi ezincencethayo zethusi\x + 15.16.\x*.
\v 20 LoZekhariya loAziyeli loShemiramothi loJehiyeli loUni loEliyabi loMahaseya loBhenaya belezigubhu zezintambo\x + 15.16.\x* ngeAlamothi\x + Hlab. 48.14.\x*.
\v 21 LoMathithiya loElifelehu loMikineya loObedi-Edoma loJeyiyeli loAzaziya\x + 15.21.\x* belamachacho\x + 15.16.\x* ngeSheminithi ukukhokhela\x + 23.4.\x*.
\v 22 LoKenaniya induna yamaLevi emthwalweni, wafundisa ngokuhlabelela ngoba wayeyingcitshi.
\v 23 LoBerekiya loElkana babengabagcini bamasango omtshokotsho.
\v 24 LoShebaniya loJoshafati loNethaneli loAmasayi loZekhariya loBhenaya loEliyezeri abapristi bakhalisa izimpondo phambi komtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu. LoObedi-Edoma loJehiya babengabagcinimasango bomtshokotsho\x + 15.28. 16.6. Nani 10.8,10. 2 Lan. 5.12,13. 7.6. 13.14. 29.26,27,28. Ezra 3.10. Neh. 12.35,41.\x*.
\p
\v 25 Kwasekusithi uDavida labadala bakoIsrayeli lenduna zezinkulungwane bahamba ukwenyusa umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* uvela endlini kaObedi-Edoma ngentokozo\x + 2 Sam. 6.12-15.\x*.
\v 26 Kwasekusithi uNkulunkulu ewasiza amaLevi ayewuthwele umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd*, banikela umhlatshelo wamajongosi ayisikhombisa lenqama eziyisikhombisa\x + Nani 23.1. Jobe 42.8.\x*.
\v 27 Njalo uDavida wayegqoke isembatho selembu elicolekileyo kakhulu, lawo wonke amaLevi ayewuthwele umtshokotsho labahlabeleli loKenaniya induna yomthwalo wabahlabeleli; uDavida-ke wayegqoke \w i-efodi\w** yelembu elicolekileyo\x + 4.21. 2 Lan. 2.14. 3.14. 5.12. Esta 1.6. 8.15. Hez. 27.16.\x*.
\v 28 Ngakho uIsrayeli wonke wawenyusa umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* ngokumemeza langokukhala kophondo lwenqama\x + Eks. 19.16. 2 Sam. 6.15. Hlab. 81.3. 2 Lan. 15.14.\x*, langezimpondo\x + 15.24.\x*, langezinsimbi ezincencethayo\x + 15.16.\x*, besenza umsindo ngezigubhu zezintambo\x + 15.16.\x* lamachacho\x + 15.16.\x*.
\p
\v 29 Kwasekusithi lapho umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* ufika emzini kaDavida, uMikhali indodakazi kaSawuli walunguza ngewindi wabona inkosi uDavida esina edlala, wamdelela enhliziyweni yakhe\x + 16.3,2 Sam. 6.16-19.\x*.